                    <h1 class="article-title">How Much Does It Cost To Train A Dog? Training Prices Explained</h1>
                    <p class="article-intro">
                        Training your dog is an important thing to think about whether you’ve had your furry friend for a while or have recently added a new pup to your family. 
                        There are plenty of benefits to dog training that can increase your bond with your dog and their overall happiness.
                        However, deciding how to train your dog and figuring out the costs of a training regiment can be overwhelming for some owners. This is why we’re here to help you out.
                        Below, we discuss the complete benefits of training your dog and break down the different factors that go into dog training costs. We’ll also be sure to give you an average amount of the expected dog training cost for the most popular types of training methods so you can make an informed decision that benefits both you and your pup.
                    </p>
